    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h2><p>教会别人是最好的学习方式，俗话说“好记性不如烂笔头”，做笔记可以提升自己的写作、总结能力，所以养成写博客的好习惯对自己是很有意的。写博客除了可以用市面上CSDN、博客园、简书、掘金等平台，也可以搭建一套自己的博客，本文着重讲一下使用hexo搭建博客。</p><p>目前较多人采用的博客搭建方案各有优缺点，有如下几种：</p><ul><li>Git+Github+Markdown+jekyll （免费）</li><li>Git+Github+Markdown+hexo （免费）</li><li>虚拟主机＋插件＋Wordpress （付费）</li></ul><h2 id="搭建环境"><a href="#搭建环境" class="headerlink" title="搭建环境"></a>搭建环境</h2><h3 id="安装Node"><a href="#安装Node" class="headerlink" title="安装Node"></a>安装Node</h3><p>Node.js用来生成静态页面</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">Node.js</a>下载相应平台的最新版本，然后安装即可</p></li><li><p>使用<code>Homebrew</code>安装</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">安装</span></span><br><span class="line">brew install node</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看版本</span></span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="安装Git"><a href="#安装Git" class="headerlink" title="安装Git"></a>安装Git</h3><p>把本地的hexo内容提交到github上去. 安装Xcode就自带有Git</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">Git</a>下载最新版本，然后安装即可</p></li><li><p>使用<code>Homebrew</code>安装</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">安装</span></span><br><span class="line">brew install git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看版本</span></span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="安装HEXO"><a href="#安装HEXO" class="headerlink" title="安装HEXO"></a>安装HEXO</h3><p>Node和Git都安装好后，可执行如下命令安装<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">Hexo</a>：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">安装</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo npm install -g hexo</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看版本</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="hexo创建本地博客"><a href="#hexo创建本地博客" class="headerlink" title="hexo创建本地博客"></a>hexo创建本地博客</h2><h3 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h3><p>创建一个文件夹，如：Blog，cd到Blog里执行一下命令。然后它会自动在Blog文件夹下生成一些配置文件，这个Blog文件夹就是博客的根目录。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">创建本地博客</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地预览"><a href="#本地预览" class="headerlink" title="本地预览"></a>本地预览</h3><ul><li><p>通过以下命令启动本地服务，进行预览调试</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">清除缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">hexo generate生成静态页面，会在当前目录下生成一个新的叫做public的文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">hexo server启动本地服务，进行文章预览调试</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>浏览器输入<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a>查看效果</p></li><li><p>常见错误：</p><ul><li><p>报错：<code>ERROR Plugin load failed: hexo-server</code></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo npm install hexo-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>报错：</code>Usage: hexo<Command> ….  `          </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-server --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>[http://localhost:4000](http://localhost:4000)打不开或者内容为空</code> </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-ejs --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-marked --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="更改主题"><a href="#更改主题" class="headerlink" title="更改主题"></a>更改主题</h3><ul><li><p>刚创建的博客默认使用的主题是<code>landscape</code>，去<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">主题集合</a>中挑选自己喜欢的样式，我使用的是 <a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next">hexo-theme-next</a></p></li><li><p>手动前往 <a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next">hexo-theme-next</a>下载，下载完成之后放到<code>Blog/themes</code>目录下；</p><p>或在<code>Bolg</code>目录文件下终端输入一下命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="built_in">cd</span>到Blog里执行命令</span></span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code>下<code>_config.yml</code>文件，修改<code>theme: landscape为theme: next</code>，前提是你已经下载完了next主题，然后本地预览查看效果  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105131451.png" style="zoom:43%;" /></p></li></ul><h3 id="主题设定"><a href="#主题设定" class="headerlink" title="主题设定"></a>主题设定</h3><ul><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code>下站点配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，修改名称、描述、作者、语言等主要配置项；  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105133820.png" style="zoom:43%;" /></p></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg/themes/next</code>下主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，修改 Scheme、菜单、侧边栏、头像等配置项；<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/getting-started.html">Next主题官网</a><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105135353.png" style="zoom:60%;" /></p></li></ul><h2 id="部署到GitHub"><a href="#部署到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="部署到GitHub"></a>部署到GitHub</h2><h3 id="创建项目"><a href="#创建项目" class="headerlink" title="创建项目"></a>创建项目</h3><ul><li>登录Github创建一个新项目，项目名必须为： `用户名.github.io  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105140929.png"/></li></ul><h3 id="修改配置文件"><a href="#修改配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改配置文件"></a>修改配置文件</h3><ul><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code>下站点配置文件<code>_config.yml</code></p></li><li><p>hexo在2点几的版本中type: github。之后的版本是type: git  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105142701.png" style="zoom:43%;" /></p></li></ul><h3 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h3><ul><li><p>执行如下命令安装插件后才能使用git部署</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>每次部署的步骤，都可按以下三步来进行。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">清除缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">重新生成静态文件，hexo generate</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">部署发布到Github，hexo deploy</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="博客发布"><a href="#博客发布" class="headerlink" title="博客发布"></a>博客发布</h2><ul><li><p>进入<code>Bolg</code>目录下，执行以下命令</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">新建文章</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new post &quot;文章名称&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>这时Bolg\source\ _posts下可以看到刚新建的”文章名称.md”文件</p></li><li><p>打开文件，使用Markdown语法编辑博客。</p></li><li><p>编辑完成后，先本地预览然后部署到github上</p></li></ul><h2 id="接入其他实用功能"><a href="#接入其他实用功能" class="headerlink" title="接入其他实用功能"></a>接入其他实用功能</h2><h3 id="添加-RSS-输出功能"><a href="#添加-RSS-输出功能" class="headerlink" title="添加 RSS 输出功能"></a>添加 RSS 输出功能<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105155820.png" style="zoom:5%;" /></h3><p>对于 <code>RSS</code> 输出功能，<code>Hexo</code> 已经有一个现成的插件可以用，那就是 <a href="https://link.jianshu.com/?t=https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-generator-feed">hexo-generator-feed</a> ，下面就来分享一下使用方法。</p><ul><li><p>首先打开终端 <code>cd</code> 到本地的 <code>Bolg</code> 目录下，输入以下命令安装 <code>RSS</code> 插件。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code> 根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，加入以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">feed:</span><br><span class="line">type: atom</span><br><span class="line">path: atom.xml</span><br><span class="line">limit: 20</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg/themes/next</code>下主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，设置 <code>RSS</code> 地址：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rss: /atom.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>最后打开终端 <code>cd</code> 到本地的 <code>Bolg</code> 目录下，输入以下命令重新部署一下博客 。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="Gitment评论系统"><a href="#Gitment评论系统" class="headerlink" title="Gitment评论系统"></a>Gitment评论系统</h3><p>我选择接入<a href="https://github.com/imsun/gitment">Gitment</a>，当然你也可以官方文档 <a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/third-party-services.html">http://theme-next.iissnan.com/third-party-services.html</a> 接入其它三方评论系统。</p><h4 id="注册Github-OAuth-Application"><a href="#注册Github-OAuth-Application" class="headerlink" title="注册Github OAuth Application"></a>注册Github OAuth Application</h4><p>登录Github<code>-&gt;</code>点击头像<code>-&gt;</code>Settings<code>-&gt;</code>Developer settings<code>-&gt;</code>Oauth Apps<code>-&gt;</code>New OAuth App`</p><p><strong>Application name</strong>:随便写</p><p><strong>Homepage URL</strong>:这个也可以随意写,就写你的博客地址就行</p><p><strong>Application description</strong>:描述,也可以随意写</p><p><strong>Authorization callback URL</strong>:这个必须写你的博客地址</p><p>​       `得到client_id、client_secret信息，下面要用到。</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105172404.png" style="zoom:33%;" /><p>  <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201105173458.png"></p><h4 id="安装Gitment"><a href="#安装Gitment" class="headerlink" title="安装Gitment"></a>安装Gitment</h4><ul><li><p>首先打开终端 <code>cd</code> 到本地的 <code>Bolg</code> 目录下，输入以下命令安装。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save gitment</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改主题配置 <code>themes/next/_config.yml</code>:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Introduction: https://imsun.net/posts/gitment-introduction/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">gitment:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>                  <span class="comment">#是否启用评论</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">githubID:</span> <span class="string">FuJunZhi</span>            <span class="comment">#在浏览器中打开：https://api.github.com/users/GitHub用户名，来获取对应数据id </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">FuJunZhi.github.io</span>      <span class="comment">#保存评论的库，当前博客或者重新创建</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ClientID:</span> <span class="string">------</span>              <span class="comment">#OAuth Application时获取的</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ClientSecret:</span> <span class="string">------</span>          <span class="comment">#OAuth Application时获取的</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">lazy:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>                   <span class="comment">#是否懒加载评论框,true：评论框默认收起</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>懒加载按钮显示的文字设置：</p><p>在主题<code>themes/next/languages/en.yml</code>文件中添加：</p><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitmentbutton: Show comments <span class="keyword">from</span> Gitment </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在主题<code>themes/next/languages/zh-Hans.yml</code>、<code>themes/next/languages/zh-CN.yml</code>文件中添加：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitmentbutton: 显示 Gitment 评论 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>懒加载按钮div及事件配置</p><p>在主题<code>layout/_partials/comments.swig</code>文件中添加：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% elseif theme.gitment.enable %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% if theme.gitment.lazy %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">onclick</span>=<span class="string">&quot;ShowGitment()&quot;</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;gitment-display-button&quot;</span>&gt;</span>&#123;&#123; __(&#x27;gitmentbutton&#x27;) &#125;&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;gitment-container&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;display:none&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% else %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;gitment-container&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>对应页面生成JS代码配置</p><p>在主题<code>layout/_third-party/comments/</code>目录下中添加文件``gitment.swig`：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% if theme.gitment.enable %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% set owner = theme.gitment.githubID %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% set repo = theme.gitment.repo %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% set cid = theme.gitment.ClientID %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% set cs = theme.gitment.ClientSecret %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-gitment@1/default.css&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-gitment@1/gitment.browser.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% if not theme.gitment.lazy %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text/javascript&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">             <span class="keyword">var</span> gitment = <span class="keyword">new</span> Gitment(&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">                id: <span class="built_in">document</span>.location.href, </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                 owner: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">owner</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                 repo: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">repo</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line">                 oauth: &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                     client_id: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">cid</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                     client_secret: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">cs</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line">                 &#125;&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">             gitment.render(<span class="string">&#x27;gitment-container&#x27;</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% else %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text/javascript&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">             <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">ShowGitment</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">                 <span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">&quot;gitment-display-button&quot;</span>).style.display = <span class="string">&quot;none&quot;</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">                 <span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">&quot;gitment-container&quot;</span>).style.display = <span class="string">&quot;block&quot;</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">                 <span class="keyword">var</span> gitment = <span class="keyword">new</span> Gitment(&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">                     id: <span class="built_in">document</span>.location.href, </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                     owner: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">owner</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                     repo: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">repo</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line">                     oauth: &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                         client_id: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">cid</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="handlebars"><span class="xml">                         client_secret: &#x27;</span><span class="template-variable">&#123;&#123;<span class="name">cs</span>&#125;&#125;</span><span class="xml">&#x27;,</span></span></span><br><span class="line">                     &#125;&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">                 gitment.render(<span class="string">&#x27;gitment-container&#x27;</span>);</span></span><br><span class="line">             &#125;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> &#123;% endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在主题下<code>layout/_third-party/comments/index.swig</code>文件中引入``gitment.swig`文件：</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% <span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&#x27;gitment.swig&#x27;</span> %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置CSS样式</p><p>在主题下<code>source/css/_common/components/third-party/</code>目录下添加<code>gitment.styl</code>文件，设置button的样式：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#gitment-display-button</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">display</span>: inline-block;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">padding</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">15px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#0a9caf</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">cursor</span>: pointer;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">14px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">border</span>: <span class="number">1px</span> solid <span class="number">#0a9caf</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">border-radius</span>: <span class="number">4px</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="selector-id">#gitment-display-button</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#fff</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="number">#0a9caf</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在主题下 <code>source/css/_common/components/third-party/third-party.styl</code>文件中引入相应的CSS样式</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@import</span> <span class="string">&quot;gitment&quot;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h4 id="常见问题"><a href="#常见问题" class="headerlink" title="常见问题"></a>常见问题</h4><ul><li><p>修改<code>themes/next/_config.yml</code>这个文件时，格式要正确。另外，repo是你要想创建issues的仓库，完全可以跟博文所放的仓库不一个。id就写自己的github用户名就可以，这个用户名跟repo必须匹配。</p></li><li><p>Error: Not Found问题，repo库填写问题，<a href="https://link.jianshu.com/?t=https://github.com/imsun/gitment/issues/18">详见gitment issues 18</a>；</p></li><li><p>同一篇文章需要<a href="https://github.com/imsun/gitment/issues/68">初始化comment两次的问题</a>，解决方法就是<code>gitment.swig</code>里id弄成<code>window.location.pathname</code>而不是<code>document.location.href</code>。</p></li><li><p>其他问题， <a href="https://github.com/imsun/gitment/issues">参见作者项目的Issue </a></p></li><li><p>object ProgressEvent</p><p>出现这个问题是由于作者在<code>gitment.browser.js</code>中硬编码了自己的服务器人证域名:<code>https://gh-oauth.imsun.net</code>，现在域名过期了,要么自己搭一个认证服务器，要么可以用其他人的，在gitment的issues里面找到了答案:<a href="https://github.com/imsun/gitment/issues/175">#175</a>,需要把Hexo你所用的主题中的引用文件给改一下，我用的是next主题,改动方法如下:</p><p> 修改`themes/next/layout/_third-party/comments/gitment.swig</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#旧配置</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://imsun.github.io/gitment/style/default.css&quot;&gt; --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- &lt;script src=&quot;https://imsun.github.io/gitment/dist/gitment.browser.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt; --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">#新配置</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-gitment@1/default.css&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/theme-next/theme-next-gitment@1/gitment.browser.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="访问量"><a href="#访问量" class="headerlink" title="访问量"></a>访问量</h3><p><a href="http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/">不蒜子访问量统计</a></p><h3 id="字数统计、阅读速度"><a href="#字数统计、阅读速度" class="headerlink" title="字数统计、阅读速度"></a>字数统计、阅读速度</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/willin/hexo-wordcount">hexo-wordcount</a></p><h3 id="本地搜索"><a href="#本地搜索" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索"></a>本地搜索</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-generator-searchdb">hexo-generator-searchdb</a></p><h3 id="Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌"><a href="#Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌" class="headerlink" title="Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌"></a>Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌</h3><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/8c0707ce5da4">Hexo博客收录百度和谷歌</a></p><h3 id="博客快速压缩"><a href="#博客快速压缩" class="headerlink" title="博客快速压缩"></a>博客快速压缩</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/chenzhutian/hexo-all-minifier">博客压缩插件</a>集成了对 html、css、js、image 的优化，安装上此模块后，只要在根目录下的_config.yml文件中加上如下字段就可对博客所有内容进行压缩。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">html_minifier:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  ignore_error: false</span><br><span class="line">  exclude:</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">css_minifier:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  exclude:</span><br><span class="line">    - &#x27;*.min.css&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">js_minifier:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  mangle: true</span><br><span class="line">  output:</span><br><span class="line">  compress:</span><br><span class="line">  exclude:</span><br><span class="line">    - &#x27;*.min.js&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">image_minifier:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  interlaced: false</span><br><span class="line">  multipass: false</span><br><span class="line">  optimizationLevel: 2</span><br><span class="line">  pngquant: false</span><br><span class="line">  progressive: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="文章链接唯一持久化"><a href="#文章链接唯一持久化" class="headerlink" title="文章链接唯一持久化"></a>文章链接唯一持久化</h3><p>由于博客需要更改文章题目或者变更文章发布时间，在默认设置下，文章链接都会改变，不利于搜索引擎收录，也不利于分享。唯一永久链接才是更好的选择。</p><ul><li><p>首先打开终端 <code>cd</code> 到本地的 <code>Bolg</code> 目录下，输入以下命令安装插件。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<code>Bolg</code> 根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，加入以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">permalink: post/:abbrlink.html</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">permalink: posts/:abbrlink/</span></span><br><span class="line">abbrlink:</span><br><span class="line">  alg: crc32  # 算法：crc16(default) and crc32</span><br><span class="line">  rep: hex    # 进制：dec(default) and hex</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="一键初始化评论"><a href="#一键初始化评论" class="headerlink" title="一键初始化评论"></a>一键初始化评论</h3><ul><li><p>配置正确的文章，第一次显示，提示还没有初始化；文章作者需要登陆GitHub授权后，会显示初始化按钮，如下图：<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201106161344.png" style="zoom:50%;" /></p></li><li><p>点击初始化按钮后注意，不要多点按钮，否则issues出现多条一样的)，如果正常就会出现下图所示：<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FuJunZhi/BlogResources@main/2020/images/20201106161548.png"></p></li><li><p><strong>可以通过<a href="https://draveness.me/git-comments-initialize/">自动初始化 Gitalk 和 Gitment 评论</a>实现<a href="https://github.com/imsun/gitment/issues/5">所有文章一键初始化</a></strong>  </p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
